Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:57.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}淡觅儚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:15.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}顿足仰天  深际蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:26.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}揽贫英至
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:33.18,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}爱恋难舍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:38.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯笑比心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:44.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只君存依
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:49.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}开往明悉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:02:02.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥律破晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:18.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}心渗醉情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:41.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみに　試されるたび  少しずつ　強くなってく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:57.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ありふれた　毎日の中　夢のつづき　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:15.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}歩きつかれて　見上げた空  深く　どこまでも　Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:26.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ちっぽけな自分　抱きしめて  それでも　進んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:33.18,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:38.90,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}笑顔を伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:44.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:49.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}光が生まれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:02:02.36,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥かなる　優しい調べ  遠い宇宙　越えて届くの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:18.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}胸の奥　かけがえのない  甘い痛み  満ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,======================ED======================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.31,0:24:34.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏に流れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.36,0:24:37.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}制服の群れに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:43.08,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}逆らうよに　自転車の
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:47.33,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}ペダル　思いきり踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:51.99,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放課後のグランドの脇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:55.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}金網をくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:25:00.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年　見つけた　ひまわりは
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.99,0:25:05.40,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年より　誇らしげに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.43,0:25:08.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}空を見上げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.66,0:25:14.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}折れないように　枯れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.22,0:25:17.99,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}涙に出来たなら
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:24.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明日は何かが変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.59,0:25:31.99,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}雨降る日は　雨に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:36.43,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}あの　ひまわりみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.60,0:25:40.66,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}まっすぐ　背を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:47.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}今日は揺れていたって、いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.31,0:24:34.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏下  逆行在流动的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.36,0:24:37.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}身着制服的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:43.08,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}尽情地  蹬踩着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:47.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}自行车的脚踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:51.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放学后  操场边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:55.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}钻过铁丝网
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:25:00.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年发现的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.99,0:25:05.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}比以往还要骄傲地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.43,0:25:08.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.66,0:25:14.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}不屈不挠  不会枯萎地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.22,0:25:17.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}若是放声哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:24.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明天又会变得怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.59,0:25:31.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}下雨的日子  在雨中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:36.43,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}就像那朵向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.60,0:25:40.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}挺直了腰杆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:47.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}哪怕今日有所动摇  也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:14.86,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.35,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:27.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:31.95,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(480,360)\fs29}终路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.88,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:39.08,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)\fs20}因事全校停课  成增小学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的理由  只是觉得该往南走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.85,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始的两天只顾着拉开距离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:44.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就开始找过夜的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:49.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不用花钱  又能挡雨遮风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:53.44,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又不引人注目的安全地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.18,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头好轻  后背好热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.29,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.47,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可以养它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.77,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}值班室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:21.23,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.37,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…一定会好好照顾它的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.12,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想个名字才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.94,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就叫「校长」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:39.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:42.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它嘴巴下面有块地方长得像胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个要用来干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.14,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断启动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:52.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人只要一开门  电极就会分离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断回路  自动启动拨号装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以多做几个布置起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:05.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能根据来电号码的差异\N得知敌人是从哪个方向入侵的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:06.06,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.75,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.03,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.09,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:27.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:29.89,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.71,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  钱…还够用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:41.34,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  住这里的话也不用交煤电费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.62,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我们的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.53,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.73,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成增小学的幽灵对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.12,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.88,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是总有个白发女孩站在屋顶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:13.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该去跟警察说一声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.48,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用没用  说了也白说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.05,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在这世道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.18,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成增小学…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.26,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含税一共740日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.11,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.19,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.11,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:32.19,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  不是有脚的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.86,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浅羽拜托我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.94,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我把这个包给他拿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.34,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.48,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没骗你  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽不会告诉别人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:44.67,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}剃刀 1500\N  猫罐头×2 1200\N合计 2700
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没被怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  就只是被他抱住推倒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:07.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了  快把那东西收起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.14,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}喂喂  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}喂喂  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.40,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去便利店了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:24.44,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果发现从杯面到牙粉全都涨价了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.48,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:33.34,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我…我的分你一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.53,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.42,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没跟你说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:46.23,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得很不甘心于是就在那白看了会书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  买了猫罐头和剃刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:51.14,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.69,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没被怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.05,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想用刀杀了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:07.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.37,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这话的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快逃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  把校长带着！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟它一起走！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:22.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:26.78,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.15,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把校长带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.44,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走  我一会就来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.83,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.48,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把校长带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:43.06,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.19,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:45.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:00.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.26,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没被怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:25.71,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.51,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本…根本就没被他怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事无所谓啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关我什么事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一遍又一遍  说得人烦都烦死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.47,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了照顾你我费心尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:43.89,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.48,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再让我看见你这张脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:13.67,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想用刀杀了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:28.09,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己回基地去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.61,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起鼻血你就自己擦吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我说得有些太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.44,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.62,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子应该饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下个镇上去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.12,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不走  我要等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.17,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等谁  基地的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.75,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:59.79,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  说得过分了是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.89,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.05,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.34,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:19.83,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:20.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:24.18,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽没来  我要等他来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:29.43,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽他啊  他说他在前面的桥那边等你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.58,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Green Light{\r}\N许可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.94,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}茶馆  梦寐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙黄白毫是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(264,441)\fs20}Orange Pekoe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:39.42,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}因故暂停营业。\N梦寐茶馆店主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.06,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了橙黄白毫和草莓芭菲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:43.11,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好像是有那种红茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  伊里野  我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.58,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说取材后如果能写成一篇报道\N就能跟浅羽一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.49,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.07,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:12.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Buddy Spike{\r}\N锁定友机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.43,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险  快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.43,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坂  你会跳MayimMayim吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟椎名学了跳法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也做了很多的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在篝火晚会上跟浅羽\N跳MayimMayim的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.24,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坂你知道篝火晚会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:34.43,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  今天是几月几日？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.78,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:42.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊  今天是九月二十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.95,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天是篝火晚会的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:51.23,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榎本说那天不会安排我出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坂你会跳MayimMayim吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:02.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:03.61,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.08,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:08.84,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:13.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.15,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道会有人来监视
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:19.79,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  今天是几号？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.31,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期的第一个星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟浅羽约的时间是十点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.16,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看现在还不到七点\N电影是十点半开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:42.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.19,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎么等浅羽也不会来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:46.97,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.31,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开啦  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  等很久了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:05.11,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.27,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:07.91,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:17.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.32,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  你走开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.40,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  那边的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.46,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我认为外人不适合插嘴\N所以只是默默观望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我实在是忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.80,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不是在等你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.06,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  伊里野是在等浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:49.16,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶快去把那个叫浅羽的家伙带来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.47,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在很远的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:58.91,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那就打电话嘛  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.93,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接跟他通话的话  她总该接受了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.45,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛  这突然是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.32,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话给伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:14.09,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  你打电话是想干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  是浅羽给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他托我转交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.31,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.03,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  伊里野  我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  听声音就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.35,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这么晚了真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.93,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该早点给你打电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.95,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  你现在人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.27,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在有点远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后…那之后发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:07.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.18,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我暂时还回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:11.40,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.97,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能陪你去看电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:17.71,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉  你一直…一直在等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:22.62,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  你明天会去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:29.86,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:34.16,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就  明天学校见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.17,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.60,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.61,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天还能跟浅羽说到话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我有来等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.75,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你们可以住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:59.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过明天我要把你们交给警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.80,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这样做是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:04.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  天一亮我们马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:05.99,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会给你添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:09.52,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我们现在就走  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:10.71,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们准备去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:12.60,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去亲戚的奶奶家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:13.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:16.91,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这一直往南  有个叫苑木泽的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近还有个海水浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你们打算怎么去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.49,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离终点站都还有段距离啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:27.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了电车就坐巴士去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  巴士今天就停运了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:32.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车从昨天起就结束一般旅客载运了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记现在是在战争中了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:39.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的线路已经被自卫军管制了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料也有限制啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:48.03,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子的头发为什么是白色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.62,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:51.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:52.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.47,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为说了  可能会给你带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.60,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  就让我告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.51,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想扯上什么是非之事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:09.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的  之后你们发生什么事我可都不管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.84,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也会说不知道\N就算被拷问也不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:13.63,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷问？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:19.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来做个试验  看你有多可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:19.80,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:20.85,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.37,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:35.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚终于到了军用列车第一号开始启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.95,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定会在凌晨一点三十二分经过本站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:42.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}Tally{\r}\N目视敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一列由电脑控制的无人列车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:49.53,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能掌握好平交道的停止信号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:53.50,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就能把速度降低到可以让你们跳上车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:20:59.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再跑快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:04.35,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我数一 二 三！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.79,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23}Friendly{\r}\N友军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.29,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉嘉会游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.65,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:31.52,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榎本说去学校的话就能在游泳池里游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:33.59,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确像是榎本会说的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:37.24,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不去学校  不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你想去游泳池游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:40.52,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:44.60,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就偷偷溜进去游就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:50.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不断尝试\N发现用压缩的方式就能跟艾莉嘉说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:53.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使变成幽灵也能交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:54.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「压缩」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.42,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个地方加上许多意义后进行压缩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.99,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟汉字一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:08.11,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们平常都聊些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:10.80,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那个幽…艾莉嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.18,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:22.40,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:23.34,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:40.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:55.60,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:57.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:02.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:09.67,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了  从明天开始我要去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:15.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:16.45,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榎本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:19.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直说不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:21.13,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:23.17,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不答应我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:26.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始我要去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:27.05,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:38.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:54.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江  我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:57.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直  洗澡水马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:23:59.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先把那身衣服脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:02.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  不快点是会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:05.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把这边的小姐背到屋里去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:09.48,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点换了衣服到这边来  我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:13.95,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  突然打电话过来 可把我给吓坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.86,0:24:21.58,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  可真慢啊


